name: Concrete Compressive Strength
abstract: Concrete is the most important material in civil engineering. The concrete compressive strength is a highly nonlinear function of age and ingredients.

intro_paper.title: Modeling of strength of high-performance concrete using artificial neural networks
intro_paper.venue: Cement and Concrete Research, Vol. 28, No. 12
